name: ✨Chonky✨ The Culinary Adventurer
description:
This is Chonky
he is a Burbuntois adventurer
This is his first timers venturing away from his chonkyhole
roam the wurld cooking and tossing for hungry adventurers.
make your stomach rumble and start a fire
he will come to your aid

First ever Digital drawing, made it in 2019.
make it in PaintToolSai
